               </persName>/ <persName>Kristern Lawss<ex>øn</ex>
               </persName>/ <persName>Reymer Powelss<ex>øn</ex>
               </persName> oc <persName>Jessæ Jeppss<ex>øn</ex>
               </persName> ewinælig m<ex>eth</ex> gwdh ♦</p>
        <p n="a#2">wi kwngøræ th<ex>et</ex> allæ mæ<ex>n</ex> aar æfter Gwz byrdh m°cd°xxxiiij
               hwidæ tiisdagh po <placeName>Wænsh<ex>e</ex>r<ex>es</ex> thing </placeName> for os oc
